latestIgtvVideos.title: New Beginnings!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
We're thrilled to reveal our refreshed brand identity. While this is a crucial change from an optic point of view, however, our core beliefs remain the same. The new identity had to satisfy all of the current expectations of what our brand stands for while simultaneously moving the brand forward across various new business verticals. We aim to present ourselves better and cater to you with better services in times to come. 

This marks a significant milestone in our journey, providing an opportunity to reflect on everything that the brand stood for and everything that we aspire to become as we move forward into an exciting future. We will have incremental advancements to help our clients associate with the brand with an experience like never before in the months to come.

Today, we are bigger and better — our family consists of highly trained and experienced individuals and a growing client portfolio that we are certainly proud to serve.

Looking forward to unfold new chapters as the new journey begins.

#AliyaBaig #newbrandidentity #newbeginnings #nextlevel #10years #decadeofhappiness
